These are tutorial-friendly replacement files for your fork.

Files included:
- index.html
- index.js

They keep the same core idea:
- HTML creates the canvas and text
- JavaScript finds those HTML elements and updates them

Notes:
- The styling is simplified a little so the teaching version is easier to read.
- The JavaScript behaviour stays very close to the original project.
- The code includes balanced beginner comments instead of commenting every line.